@Property_Viewing_Slots_API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5124

###

### Book a property viewing
POST {{Property_Viewing_Slots_API_HostAddress}}/propertyviewing/book
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "propertyId": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
  "userId": "f1e2d3c4-b5a6-7890-abcd-ef0987654321",
  "startTime": "2026-07-10T10:00:00"
}

###

### Search viewings for a property within a date range
GET {{Property_Viewing_Slots_API_HostAddress}}/propertyviewing/search?propertyId=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890&startDate=2026-07-01T00:00:00&endDate=2026-07-31T23:59:59
Accept: application/json

###
